  "best_review_details": [
    {
      "text": "We were having problems with closing our front door, and subsequently opening it, which became a real issue one evening. Spoke to Steve on the phone, and he gave us some options to try to resolve the problem, and he then came out to us the following day and fixed it. He also asked if all of our other locks were ok once he’d finished. We’d been having a few minor issues with our bathroom lock, so h",
      "author": "Debbie",
      "rating": 5,
      "source": "google"
    },
    {
      "text": "I needed a locksmith to change my mum's locks as she was left vulnerable. I can't recommend The Lock Dr enough! From the time I called to the time the job was complete was around 45 minutes! Exceptional service! Will 100% use again!! Thank you for making my mum safe!",
      "author": "Mark",
      "rating": 5,
      "source": "google"
    },
    {
      "text": "I called Steve out for a lock that had seized all weekend. Typically, he arrives and the lock finally unlocks by itself! Got some great advice on how I can help stop this happening again, thank you so much for your time",
      "author": "Mike",
      "rating": 5,
      "source": "google"
    }
  ],
